detaileddescription.para: Class for holding model parameters. Defines the basic container and get/set functions for the model parameters. Originally adapted from SUfit version (the connection is basically gone now though.)
Authors (add name and date if you modify):

simplesect.para: 2014 Aug: Went through and cut out some stuff that seemed unused: removed the old ModelParametersBase class that didn't do much; removed the virtualisation since nothing derives from this class at the moment; incorporated the proper error handling system; put class definitions into a seperate source file.
